<div type="definition">
<p>PERFECTLY ROUND THING that CAN BE MOVED.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The word for a football is qiú 毬, but the word is exceedingly rare.</p>
<p>NB: Qiú 球 is current in pre-Buddhist Chinese only as referring to a music stone made of jade.</p>
        </div>
